  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个系统架构图，核心是文件中心节点，四个模块围绕它分布：Writer在上方，Scholar在左，Vis在右，Code在下方。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，菱形布局。那这四个模块和中心文件的关系是双向的吗？还是单向依赖？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "双向的，每个模块既向FilesCenter推送，也从它拉取。另外这四个模块之间还有交叉协作：Scholar可以驱动Writer，Writer能触发Code，Code再连接Vis，Vis又能回流到Writer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScholarLeft",
        "WriterTop",
        "CodeBottom",
        "VisRight"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，菱形加交叉连线已经画好。现在需要区分视觉层级，我打算把FilesCenter设为核心样式，四个模块用统一模块样式，你看可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom",
        "core",
        "mod"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，核心用深底色，模块用稍浅的。对了，还需要加一个AI Engine，它要同时连接这四个模块，但不直接连FilesCenter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AI",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "AI节点已添加，四条辐射线指向四个模块。AI的样式我打算用暖色边框区分，和核心、模块形成三色体系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AI",
        "ai",
        "core",
        "mod"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "检查下交叉连线，Vis到Writer的箭头方向对吗？应该是Vis反馈到Writer，不是反向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VisRight",
        "WriterTop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，刚才画反了。已修正，现在是VisRight指向WriterTop，表示可视化结果反馈给写作模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VisRight",
        "WriterTop"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在对了。再确认下样式数值：核心填充#1f2a40，模块#2e3b55，AI用#3c4f6b，边框色分别是#aac7ff和#ffcc66。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "core",
        "mod",
        "ai"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用。核心stroke-width用2px，模块和AI用1.5px，文字统一白色。整体结构：菱形四角加中心，交叉对角线，AI辐射层，三层视觉清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
